<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Primary colour</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select the primary colour of your online store. It determines the colouring of the buttons and widgets in your online store. Choose a colour from the colour picker or enter a hexadecimal value.<br>
