</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="70">6. Selecting a language</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>It is possible to create homepages with different languages independently of one another.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Selecting a language:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>CMS » ShopBuilder</strong>.<br>
→ The overview of the ShopBuilder opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select a language from the drop-down list.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click <strong>Add page</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter a name for the page.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.<br>
→ The language settings for the page will be saved automatically.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="75">7. Displaying client preview</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>On the editing page, it is possible to view the created page for the different clients (preview).</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Displaying client preview:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>CMS » ShopBuilder</strong>.<br>
→ The overview of the ShopBuilder opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select a client from the drop-down list <strong>Select client</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select a page.<br>
